## Level 1 Specification

Grade: 1  
World: Sensing  
Big Idea: Machines sense the world using inputs, not understanding.

### Assets
- Story (multi-format, multi-language)
- Concept video
- HTML interactive game
- Worksheets (PDF)
- Teacher guide

### Unlock Logic (School Mode)
IF facilitator_confirmation = true
AND game_completed = true
THEN level_status = completed

### Unlock Logic (Home Mode)
IF min_time_spent >= threshold
AND reflection_completed = true
AND game_completed = true
THEN level_status = completed
